  "title": "Accounts Assistant (Entry Level)",
  "description": "<p>Our client is a <strong>Marine and Offshore Industry.</strong> Due to business needs, they are now recruiting a Accounts Assistant to be part of their Team for ongoing transformation projects. They are located in the <strong>West </strong>- easily accessible.<br /></p><p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p><p><ul><li>Provide administrative and coordination support to the finance, project, and operations functions.</li><li>Handle <strong>complete accounting records </strong>with a solid grasp of <strong>double-entry bookkeeping</strong> principles.</li><li>Assist in the <strong>preparation and processing of customer quotations and sales orders</strong> to facilitate day-to-day finance and project activities.</li><li>Monitor and follow up on quotation status, sales order progress, and project timelines to ensure smooth execution.</li><li>Ensure systematic filing and upkeep of financial, project, and operational documentation for control and audit purposes.</li></ul></p><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Diploma in any related field</li><li>Proficient with accounting software is an advantage.</li></ul><p></p><p><em>Interested candidates who wish to apply for the advertised position, please click </em><em><strong>APPLY NOW</strong></em><em> or email an updated copy of your resume/cv.</em></p><p><em>We regret that only shortlisted candidate will be notified.</em><br /></p><p><em>Email Address: </em><a href=\"mailto:jobs@recruitpedia.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><em>jobs@recruitpedia.sg</em></a></p><p><em>Recruitpedia Pte. Ltd.</em></p><p><em>EA License No: 19C9682</em></p><p><em>EA Personnel No: R25157233 (Loh Pooi Keng)</em></p>",
